            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2a0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:12:30.23+09:00">“黃帝</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:12:38.429+09:00">是少典氏的後代，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:13:04.196+09:00">姓公孫，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:13:14.876+09:00">名軒轅。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:13:29.032+09:00">他剛出生就表現出神奇靈異的一面，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:13:37.598+09:00">很小的時候就會說話了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:13:54.376+09:00">年幼時就思維敏捷，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:14:15.239+09:00">稍大一些則純樸勤勉，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:14:23.68+09:00">成年以後能夠明辨是非。 </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:14:34.315+09:00">軒轅的時候，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:14:40.261+09:00">正處在神農氏衰落的時代。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:14:44.111+09:00">諸侯之間相互攻伐，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:15:32.845+09:00">殘害百姓，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:15:37.308+09:00">而神農氏沒有能力征討。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:15:44.373+09:00">於是軒轅就訓練士兵使用武器，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:15:57.673+09:00">來征討不來朝貢的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:16:02.708+09:00">諸侯就都俯首稱臣了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:16:08.736+09:00">可是蚩尤非常殘暴，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T19:16:09.066+09:00">誰也無法征服他。”</seg>
                </p>
